Hello!

Trying to create custom HTML + Hubl Email Template that will be using the Drag n' Drop Functionality. I've created the following module:

```{% dnd_area "main", label="Hero with Headline" %}
        &lt;!-- Section --&gt;
        {% dnd_section
           background_color='#e5e5e5',
           padding='0px',
           max_width=600,
           vertical_alignment='MIDDLE'
        %}
          {% dnd_module path='/Experience Group Templates/_modules/Hero - with headline.module' %}
          {% end_dnd_module %}
        {% end_dnd_section %}
      {% end_dnd_area %}```

Preview shows up fine, but i can't seem to publish it due to the following error:

```Error:0:0This template is missing the required tag {{ style_settings }}```

I couldn't find anything within the documentation on the variable  `{{ style_settings }}` and when viewing the  output it returns:

```          EmailCustomSettings{backgroundColor=#bbbdc0, bodyBorderColor=#cccccc, bodyBorderWidth=1, bodyBorderColorChoice=BORDER_AUTOMATIC, bodyColor=#ffffff, useEmailClientDefaultSettings=false, primaryFont=Tahoma, Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, primaryFontColor=#231f20, primaryAccentColor=#e12632, primaryFontSize=15, secondaryFont=sans-serif, secondaryFontColor=#808185, secondaryAccentColor=#231f20, secondaryFontSize=12, headingOneFont=FontStyle{size=28, fontStyle={}}, headingTwoFont=FontStyle{size=22, fontStyle={}}, linksFont=FontStyle{fontStyle={}}, emailBodyPadding=30, emailBodyWidth=600}```
 Anyone know how to solve this error?
